nodes.text: A parade was a celebratory event where people, vehicles, and even creatures would march in a ceremonial fashion to commemorate a particular event. After the planet Naboo was liberated from the Trade Federation, the Naboo and the Gungans held a parade in Theed to celebrate their victory and mark their newfound friendship. Fifteen years after the rise of the Galactic Empire, the planet Lothal celebrated Empire Day with a parade in Capital City.
